did.unittitle: District Six, Letters regarding newly elected officers; Altrusa club presidents; Joan Curtis from Nacy J. Russell

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: 1967 letter from Governor Virginia Sams concerning President's Workshop to be held April 22, 1967. 1971-1972 correspondence seems to be related to Christmas and New Year's holidays. Letter to Joan Curtis (September 29, 1974) from Nancy J. Russell, Vocational Services Chairman, concerning committee workshops at the 1974 District Six Convention in Evansville.
